List of Current NATO Standards

Introduction:
This is an extract from the NATO Standardization Document Database (NSDD) showing only the current (promulgated) documents, bearing security classification appropriate for this WEB Site. Standardization documentation started a period of transition on 1 Jan 11 and over the next 3 years or so each NATO standard should comprise:
  • a cover document containing the administrative information (a Standardization Agreement (STANAG) or a Recommendation (STANREC))
  • the standard in a separate document or set of documents (Allied Standard(s) like NATO and non-NATO Standard(s))
  • an optional set of other Standards-Related Documents (SRDs) (such as implementation guides, catalogues or national data)

During the transition period, some older documents will still be found where the standard is included in the STANAG (ie no Allied Standard visible) and a very few Standards that do not show a covering document. In the list below, please note that, occasionally, two editions of one Standard appear where one is current (just says status promulgated), but a new one has been agreed with a NATO EFFECTIVE DATE (NED) in the future (says status promulgated not effective). The status and the NED can be found by clicking the corresponding Short-Title link.

The list contains the following columns:
  • Item No: Entry Number in the list
  • Type:
    • Cov shows a cover document,
    • Std shows a standard,
    • Cov+Std shows that the standard is still included in the STANAG (no separate Standard body),
    • No Cov shows that there is a Standard with no cover document listed
  • Short Title: How the standards are known. If you click at these titles further admin. information (like status, promulgation date etc.) will be displayed
  • Lang: Shows the language the different documents are available. EN for English, FR for French
  • Long Title/Link (if document is available): This provides a description of the standard. If the corresponding document is available on line, you can click on this entry to open or download it.
  • Updated On: Latest update of the corresponding document (This is the Operating System date stamp for the document)

Number of items found:1157 and include 1062 Cover(s), 979 Standard(s) and 114 SRD(s)
